title: The.Dr.Phil.Show.2015.11.13.(PART.2).WEB-DL.x264
description:
This is Part 2 of today's show that was preempted on my local network due to news coverage of the terror attacks in Paris.

This is taken from YouTube. The video shrunken within another frame is done intentionally by the YouTube uploader so that the video gets past YouTube's copyright filter.

If they didn't do this, YouTube's system would automatically block the video.

I figured having Part 2 in this format would be better than not having it at all for the fans.

~2Maverick
